  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had very high temperature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I think self-suggestion, you know, worked on you really-- What happened when--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there-- I guess there were some doctors that-- you-- you just reminded me of something, [? though. ?] There were some doctors that were attending.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe you had some Poles on the outside, and maybe somebody would give you some medication.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or you would-- you could get some medication from-- from the outside world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you didn't, you died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I know that there was, but, you know, I was so far away from it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know about sex at that time yet, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I only learned later on about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I really-- I-- I know I heard later on that there-- there were some babies born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it's interesting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a-- a man that was living with us in the apartment, and he was my father's very good friend.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he had a crush on my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after the war, he wanted to marry my mother, because he survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But so, I guess there were-- besides, you know, all these problems and these whatever it is, I mean, there was still emotions and relationships and whatever probably formed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't [? know. ?]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did take care of kids, but that was-- that was when we were in the forests already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, maybe--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't remember any organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we used to spend time with some friends in each other's house, playing with dolls, playing doctor, playing house, I mean, you know, just regular whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
